1
00:00:42,920 --> 00:00:43,880
What are we doing for fun today?

2
00:00:44,200 --> 00:00:44,920
I'm tired today.

3
00:00:45,039 --> 00:00:45,719
I don't want to go out.

4
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:00,799
Then...

5
00:01:02,119 --> 00:01:03,719
Let's just have fun at home.

6
00:01:21,840 --> 00:01:24,799
You used to do this with Sheng Yuanzhou too, right?

7
00:01:43,599 --> 00:01:45,040
Don't be so impatient.

8
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:48,280
Honey.

9
00:01:48,959 --> 00:01:51,680
We did a lot more than just this.

10
00:01:56,879 --> 00:01:58,799
I'll go downstairs and deal with the nanny first.

11
00:01:59,439 --> 00:02:01,599
So no one disturbs us.

12
00:02:05,319 --> 00:02:05,879
Wait for me.

13
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:28,759
Happy?

14
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:39,680
After scheming for so many days...

15
00:02:39,840 --> 00:02:41,439
...just to steal it from me?

16
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:44,080
I'm just returning it to its rightful owner.

17
00:02:44,080 --> 00:02:44,840
Is that so?

18
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:46,159
Then take a look.

19
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:47,840
Is it your Key of Fate?

20
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:53,039
Where are the numbers?

21
00:02:53,199 --> 00:02:54,520
That day, in the security footage,

22
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:56,199
I saw you find the safe.

23
00:02:56,199 --> 00:02:57,599
I figured you'd pull something like this.

24
00:02:57,879 --> 00:02:59,280
You tricked me once with a fake spoon.

25
00:02:59,439 --> 00:03:00,400
Now I'm tricking you.

26
00:03:00,759 --> 00:03:01,439
We're even.

27
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:02,479
Fine.

28
00:03:04,039 --> 00:03:04,960
You win this time.

29
00:03:05,319 --> 00:03:06,759
You really didn't have to

30
00:03:06,759 --> 00:03:08,560
go through all this trouble with these petty tricks.

31
00:03:08,879 --> 00:03:11,400
It's not like I married you for love anyway.

32
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:13,759
Since you want the Key of Fate back,

33
00:03:14,199 --> 00:03:15,199
let's talk terms.

34
00:03:15,599 --> 00:03:16,479
What terms?

35
00:03:24,919 --> 00:03:27,159
Break off the engagement to Lin Siqi now.

36
00:03:27,159 --> 00:03:28,240
Get engaged to me.

37
00:03:28,599 --> 00:03:30,680
Once I'm the Sheng's daughter-in-law,

38
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:33,240
I'll hand over the Key of Fate myself.

39
00:03:33,719 --> 00:03:36,400
Getting Lin Siqi to leave Sheng Yuanzhou

40
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:38,120
is what you want too, isn't it?

41
00:03:38,439 --> 00:03:41,280
Zhang Xiaobei.

42
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:49,199
Break off the engagement.

43
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:50,280
Yes, Father.

44
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:52,919
I'll break off the engagement to Lin Siqi.

45
00:03:53,919 --> 00:03:54,400
Your reason?

46
00:03:54,639 --> 00:03:55,800
Lin Siqi may be the eldest daughter,

47
00:03:56,199 --> 00:03:57,319
but she didn't study medicine.

48
00:03:57,919 --> 00:03:58,919
Nor is she good at management.

49
00:03:59,319 --> 00:04:02,280
Also, Lin Siqi's stepmother has two sons.

50
00:04:02,719 --> 00:04:04,039
They're still young right now,

51
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:06,520
but judging by how they're being raised,

52
00:04:06,879 --> 00:04:08,000
in the future, the Lin family's business

53
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:09,919
will likely go to those two boys.

54
00:04:10,159 --> 00:04:11,039
So that means

55
00:04:11,319 --> 00:04:12,439
being engaged to Lin Siqi

56
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:14,199
doesn't help Prosperity Group

57
00:04:14,879 --> 00:04:15,879
in any way.

58
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:17,399
It's just them taking advantage of us.

59
00:04:17,839 --> 00:04:19,000
I need a helpmate.

60
00:04:20,199 --> 00:04:23,600
So I want to break off the engagement

61
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:25,959
for Jiang Lai of Wanli Construction.

62
00:04:27,199 --> 00:04:27,959
Jiang Lai.

63
00:04:28,279 --> 00:04:28,959
Yes, Father.

64
00:04:29,639 --> 00:04:31,319
Prosperity Group's main business

65
00:04:31,519 --> 00:04:32,639
is real estate.

66
00:04:32,879 --> 00:04:34,560
Wanli Construction's achievements

67
00:04:34,879 --> 00:04:35,720
are clear for all to see.

68
00:04:36,319 --> 00:04:37,600
Whether it's financial strength

69
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,319
or business support,

70
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:42,399
Jiang Lai is far better than Lin Siqi.

71
00:04:45,759 --> 00:04:47,600
I opposed you breaking off the engagement with the Lin family before

72
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:49,319
because I thought you were just being immature.

73
00:04:50,279 --> 00:04:51,120
Now it seems

74
00:04:51,399 --> 00:04:52,519
you really have grown up.

75
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:55,360
Since you have your own plan,

76
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:57,399
then from now on, your marriage

77
00:04:57,639 --> 00:04:58,759
is yours to decide.

78
00:05:00,399 --> 00:05:01,120
Thank you, Father.

79
00:05:11,959 --> 00:05:12,959
It's done.

80
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:14,560
Okay, I got it.

81
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:23,160
Hand it over.

82
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:24,680
What?

83
00:05:26,759 --> 00:05:27,920
The Key of Fate.

84
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:30,519
Your spies must've already told you everything.

85
00:05:33,439 --> 00:05:35,399
You just talked to Sheng Shizhong

86
00:05:35,399 --> 00:05:37,000
and you think you can take it back?

87
00:05:37,839 --> 00:05:39,120
It's not going to be that easy.

88
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:40,120
Then what do you want?

89
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:41,800
Simple. Announce it to the world.

90
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:46,360
That might be hard to pull off.

91
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:48,920
I have to consider the Lin family's feelings.

92
00:05:49,199 --> 00:05:50,759
Sounds like you can't let go of Lin Siqi.

93
00:05:54,279 --> 00:05:55,720
I'm thinking about you.

94
00:05:56,399 --> 00:05:58,680
The Ren'ai Hospital Oncology Center

95
00:05:58,959 --> 00:06:01,240
is being built by Wanli Construction.

96
00:06:01,519 --> 00:06:03,120
You wouldn't want, over an engagement,

97
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:04,639
to sour our relationship

98
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:06,000
and ruin the project, right?

99
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:11,480
Then what do you want?

100
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,480
Don't expect something for nothing.

101
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:15,199
I'll make sure you're satisfied.

102
00:06:28,959 --> 00:06:29,639
What's this?

103
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:30,920
Open it and see for yourself.

104
00:06:38,759 --> 00:06:39,279
Take it back.

105
00:06:41,319 --> 00:06:43,720
Jiang Lai, don't tell me you like me.

106
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:45,480
Then I advise you to give up.

107
00:06:45,879 --> 00:06:46,800
I only like Lin Siqi.

108
00:06:47,160 --> 00:06:48,079
What are you talking about?

109
00:06:48,079 --> 00:06:49,720
Don't waste your time anymore.

110
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:51,720
No matter how much money you spend,

111
00:06:52,319 --> 00:06:53,399
I still won't like you.

112
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:54,720
You're really something else.

113
00:06:54,879 --> 00:06:55,600
So narcissistic.

114
00:06:56,160 --> 00:06:57,600
I have no such intentions.

115
00:06:58,160 --> 00:06:59,439
Then why'd you treat me to dinner

116
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:01,040
and ask me to a hotel?

117
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:02,120
I was hoping

118
00:07:02,279 --> 00:07:04,480
you and Lin Siqi could go relax.

119
00:07:04,759 --> 00:07:06,079
You finally managed to take her

120
00:07:06,079 --> 00:07:07,800
away from Sheng Yuanzhou.

121
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:08,800
You need to put in more effort.

122
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,079
You're helping me,

123
00:07:12,279 --> 00:07:12,920
so what do you want out of it?

124
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,360
I want to be Mrs. Sheng.

125
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:17,399
I need Lin Siqi to leave Sheng Yuanzhou.

126
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:19,120
Let's team up.

127
00:07:20,839 --> 00:07:22,000
Each gets what they need.

128
00:07:24,639 --> 00:07:27,079
I've already arranged the hotel room for you.

129
00:07:27,199 --> 00:07:29,560
Don't screw it up when the time comes.

130
00:07:55,879 --> 00:07:57,839
Didn't think you were such a hopeless romantic.

131
00:07:59,399 --> 00:08:00,000
What?

132
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:02,360
You and Siqi usually

133
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:04,240
date like this?

134
00:08:05,279 --> 00:08:06,480
Then what do you want to do?

135
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:08,480
Nothing.

136
00:08:09,319 --> 00:08:10,639
We're not high schoolers anymore.

137
00:08:17,959 --> 00:08:19,040
No need. Hurry up and put it on.

138
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:20,040
There are people outside.

139
00:08:21,279 --> 00:08:21,959
That's enough.

140
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:23,920
It's fine. What's the big deal?

141
00:08:24,639 --> 00:08:25,759
If we're going to stir up gossip,

142
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:27,639
we need some juicy material, don't we?

143
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:31,319
Sheng Yuanzhou.

144
00:08:34,639 --> 00:08:35,519
What are you doing here?

145
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:36,919
We're here on vacation.

146
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:38,159
Vacation?

147
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,120
I invited them.

148
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:47,320
Siqi.

149
00:08:48,039 --> 00:08:48,720
What a coincidence.

150
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:50,600
You're on a date here too?

151
00:08:51,320 --> 00:08:51,919
Yeah.

152
00:08:57,279 --> 00:08:58,519
Then we won't bother you.

153
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:00,279
It's lunchtime.

154
00:09:00,519 --> 00:09:01,799
Why don't we eat together?

155
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:02,919
Maybe not.

156
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:05,159
Siqi,

157
00:09:05,720 --> 00:09:07,879
are you upset I'm with Yuanzhou?

158
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:10,240
Why won't you even eat with us?

159
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:14,639
Then see you in a bit.

160
00:09:22,919 --> 00:09:24,720
It's not like you two had real feelings.

161
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,360
So there's no need to avoid suspicion.

162
00:09:29,399 --> 00:09:30,759
A new love meets an old flame.

163
00:09:31,279 --> 00:09:32,559
And the old flame brought a new love.

164
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:35,360
How exciting.

165
00:09:44,799 --> 00:09:45,279
Thanks.

166
00:10:05,679 --> 00:10:06,879
You wouldn't know this, but

167
00:10:06,879 --> 00:10:08,480
when Yuanzhou eats fish,

168
00:10:08,919 --> 00:10:10,879
the servants pick out the bones

169
00:10:10,879 --> 00:10:12,320
one by one.

170
00:10:15,039 --> 00:10:16,679
Siqi, you know that already.

171
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:20,120
After all, you two had a marriage alliance.

172
00:10:25,240 --> 00:10:25,960
Right... yeah.

173
00:10:30,320 --> 00:10:30,879
Jiang Lai.

174
00:10:30,879 --> 00:10:32,000
Why didn't you tell me sooner

175
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:32,960
that you two are together?

176
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:34,960
Then I'd have a perfect reason to refuse.

177
00:10:35,559 --> 00:10:37,320
Yuanzhou is just too filial.

178
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:40,120
He won't resist the marriage alliance.

179
00:10:40,639 --> 00:10:42,759
If you ask me, Siqi, you're the brave one.

180
00:10:42,759 --> 00:10:45,039
If you hadn't insisted on Zhang Xiaobei,

181
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:47,240
how could I be with Sheng Yuanzhou?

182
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:49,720
But...

183
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:51,799
you haven't broken off the engagement yet.

184
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:53,000
Siqi,

185
00:10:53,240 --> 00:10:54,879
I'm so glad you don't mind.

186
00:10:57,639 --> 00:10:59,279
Then this is perfect.

187
00:11:00,399 --> 00:11:02,399
I wish you two happiness.

188
00:11:02,840 --> 00:11:03,279
Cheers.

189
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:04,559
Here.

190
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:08,720
About the marriage alliance,

191
00:11:09,159 --> 00:11:10,840
I'll tell my dad to cancel it.

192
00:11:13,559 --> 00:11:14,440
Drink a little less.

193
00:11:27,799 --> 00:11:28,519
Xiaobei,

194
00:11:28,759 --> 00:11:30,320
take better care of your girlfriend too.

195
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:32,279
Siqi's done so much for you.

196
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:34,200
I...

197
00:11:34,720 --> 00:11:35,519
I'll peel some shrimp for you.

198
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:38,720
No, no need. Um, Xiaobei,

199
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:39,440
I'll do it.

200
00:11:39,799 --> 00:11:40,960
No, I...

201
00:11:40,960 --> 00:11:42,279
I can peel them. Don't worry.

202
00:11:42,639 --> 00:11:43,559
No, I... just wait.

203
00:11:45,159 --> 00:11:46,600
Siqi can't eat seafood.

204
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:56,320
She likes sweet things.

205
00:12:15,759 --> 00:12:17,600
Sorry to interrupt. Our restaurant is hosting

206
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:18,799
a Qixi Festival couples event.

207
00:12:18,799 --> 00:12:20,279
Would any of you like to join?

208
00:12:20,759 --> 00:12:21,440
Participating couples

209
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:22,480
will receive two

210
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:23,720
free special mixed drinks.

211
00:12:24,679 --> 00:12:25,360
How do we join?

212
00:12:25,639 --> 00:12:27,159
It's simple. You just need to provide

213
00:12:27,159 --> 00:12:28,480
a photo of the couple kissing.

214
00:12:36,399 --> 00:12:37,279
Sure, we'll join.

215
00:12:37,399 --> 00:12:38,000
Come on, Yuanzhou.
